---
import PageLayout from "~/layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---
<PageLayout
  eyebrow="Openings"
  title="Join us"
  lede="We look for people who have a passion for problem solving, learning, and a willingness to experiment with new ideas and technologies."
>
  <div class="prose max-w-3xl">
    <p>All positions are located in Cambridge, MA, USA.</p>

    <h2>Prospective PhD students</h2>
    <p>
      If you are looking for PhD positions, please apply to the graduate programs at MIT
      or Harvard. We do not accept any PhD student directly into the lab — you have to
      first be admitted into a program and then choose to work with our group. We
      definitely have plenty of projects for, and welcome, rotation students from MIT or
      Harvard.
    </p>

    <h2>High school students / citizen scientists</h2>
    <p>
      If you are interested in working with us, please open an issue describing your
      interests in this GitHub repo:
      <a href="https://github.com/sensein/science4all">github.com/sensein/science4all</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>UROPs</h2>
    <p>
      If you are an undergraduate at MIT, we have several projects suited for UROP
      projects. We work through the Quest Initiative or with other faculty for such
      projects. Feel free to get in touch with us.
    </p>

    <h2>Staff / postdoc positions</h2>
    <p>None available at the moment.</p>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
